Python vs C/C++
===============

Introduction
------------

So far you have learned to use different programming languages and you have probably had rarely a chance to choose yourself. This assignment prepares you for the moment of free choice. It is supposed to make you think of the key differences of the languages used in this class: Python and C++.  

1) Where are the differences?
-----------------------------

Try to think of the most important differences of these languages, give some advantages, disadvantages and think of the scopes of application. Concentrate on the basic ideas covered in this class and write about a half a page.


2) Emphasize a difference
-------------------------

Think of a short code example where one language provides great advantages over the other. Explain in a few words how this example emphasizes one or more of the above mentioned differences.

